About Us

Meet Sheba, Shiba’s best cat friend. Shiba is on top of the world as one of the highest grossing meme coin. He gathers a lot of attention and everyone knows about him. But even with all the fame he still feels lonely at the top. He misses his beloved friend Sheba. The cat who he grew up with. Let’s reunite them and meet each other at the top of the crypto space!!

TOKEN INFORMATION

Tokenomics

100% safe decentralized project, ownership renounced and liquidity locked for 78 years.

Tax Distribution

Every transaction has a 3% tax where 2% goes to the marketing wallet and 1% to the PancakeSwap liquidity pool.

  • 3% Total Tax
  • 2% Marketing
  • 1% Liquidity

Token Distribution

Total Supply 1.000.000.000 (1B Tokens)
  • 50% Initial Burn
  • 35% Liquidity
  • 5% Marketing Wallet
  • 5% Exchange Funds (vested 1 month)
  • 5% Staking (vested 2 weeks)

How to Buy

Sheba is a decentralized experiment and, as such, we always incentivize the use of DEXs. Sheba is purchased and sold through PancakeSwap. In the future we will also be found on Uniswap and an ever-growing list of CEXs.

Don’t know how to use PancakeSwap? Watch this tutorial on How to Use PancakeSwap with MetaMask:

Quick Start Guide

1

Download & setup MetaMask or TrustWallet

Download MetaMask (a crypto wallet in the form of a browser extension) or TrustWallet (an app for your phone). After that, you will have to add the Binance Smart Chain to your network-list. (Click here for a step-by-step tutorial).

2

Buy and send BNB to Metamask or TrustWallet

Buy BNB on an exchange (i.e. Binance, Kraken, Coinbase etc.). Transfer the BNB to your MetaMask wallet address. BEP-20 addresses start with a “0x”.

3

Go to PancakeSwap and swap BNB for Sheba

Go to PancakeSwap → Trade → Exchange and connect your wallet.
Use our contract address: 0x08762be6631BeF12Efb750ff276e2e5095957AfB to select Sheba. Set the slippage tolerance to 3-5% (sometimes it may be bigger depending on the market demand for our token) and swap BNB for Sheba.

Join Our Communities

Have any questions, ideas or just want a place to make new friends? Our Sheba community welcomes you with open arms. We recommend following our social media platforms to keep up to date with all the Sheba news and announcements.
